column5: Am I nuts or did TJ not post as many Jiggy reports this year? I really enjoy reading them and seeing what inspector gadget has done next to the hi tech Lo tech getaway!
I saw 2 threads, i believe in august.He`s a very resourceful guy. A true MacGyver
TJ has posted at least five Camp Jiggy Jiggy reports this season. I think he might be waiting for us to catch up.
